                            <comment id="12892" author="juergen.hoeller" created="Thu, 7 Apr 2005 18:11:27 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Darren, have you already had a chance to look at this issue? Does this fix make 1.2 RC2, to be released on Monday?&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Juergen&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12961" author="juergen.hoeller" created="Mon, 11 Apr 2005 22:01:41 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;As this sounds plausible and spring.ftl works for me without explicit &quot;spring.&quot; prefix used in internal expressions, I&apos;ve changed this for 1.2 RC2. We can still adapt it for 1.2 final, if necessary.&lt;/p&gt;

